trans-unit.source: Enumerates the elements of a <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary`2.KeyCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 枚举 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary`2.KeyCollection" /> 的元素。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 语言的语句 (`for each` c + + 中`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 隐藏了枚举数的复杂性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建议使用 `foreach`，而不是直接操作枚举数。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.IDisposable> interface.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IDisposable> 接口。

trans-unit.source: When you have finished using the type, you should dispose of it either directly or indirectly.
trans-unit.target: 在使用完类型后，您应直接或间接释放类型。

trans-unit.source: To dispose of the type directly, call its <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> method in a`try`/`catch` block.
trans-unit.target: 若要直接释放类型，调用其<xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A>中的方法`try`/ `catch`块。

trans-unit.source: To dispose of it indirectly, use a language construct such as `using` (in C#) or `Using` (in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: 若要间接释放类型，请使用 `using`（在 C# 中）或 `Using`（在 Visual Basic 中）等语言构造。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the "Using an Object that Implements IDisposable" section in the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface topic.
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅中的"使用实现 IDisposable 的对象"部分<xref:System.IDisposable>接口主题。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器可用于读取集合中的数据，但不能用于修改基础集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 最初，枚举数定位在集合中第一个元素的前面。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 在此位置上，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>属性是不确定。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，必须调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法将枚举数前移到集合，然后再读取的值的第一个元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> property returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>属性返回相同的对象，直到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>调用。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> 设置为下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>越过的末尾的集合，枚举数定位在集合中的最后一个元素的后面和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 当枚举器位于此位置上，后续调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>还返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最后一次调用到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 无法再次将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> 设置为集合的第一个元素；必须改为创建新的枚举器实例。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合保持不变，枚举数就保持有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果对集合进行更改（如添加、修改或删除元素），则枚举数将失效且不可恢复，而且其行为是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 枚举数没有对集合的独占访问权；因此，从头到尾对一个集合进行枚举在本质上不是一个线程安全的过程。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保枚举过程中的线程安全性，可以在整个枚举过程中锁定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要允许多个线程访问集合以进行读写操作，则必须实现自己的同步。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空间中集合的默认实现是不同步的。

trans-unit.source: Gets the element at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 获取枚举数当前位置的元素。

trans-unit.source: The element in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary`2.KeyCollection" /> at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary`2.KeyCollection" /> 中位于该枚举数当前位置的元素。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> property is undefined under any of the following conditions:
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>属性未定义任何以下条件下：

trans-unit.source: The enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection, immediately after the enumerator is created.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器创建后立即，枚举数定位在集合中，第一个元素之前。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method must be called to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>必须调用方法来枚举器向前移动到集合，然后再读取的值的第一个元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, which indicates the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 上次调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`，指示集合的末尾。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> property returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>属性返回相同的对象，直到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>调用。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> 设置为下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: If the collection is modified between <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> returns the element that it is set to, even though the enumerator is invalidated.
trans-unit.target: 如果之间修改集合<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>，<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>返回到，设置的元素，即使枚举数已经无效。

trans-unit.source: For better performance, this property does not throw an exception if the enumerator is positioned before the first element or after the last element.
trans-unit.target: 为了提高性能，此属性不引发异常，如果枚举数定位的第一个元素之前或之后的最后一个元素。

trans-unit.source: Instead, the value of the property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 相反，属性的值是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary`2.KeyCollection.Enumerator" />.
trans-unit.target: 释放由 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary`2.KeyCollection.Enumerator" /> 使用的所有资源。

trans-unit.source: Advances the enumerator to the next element of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary`2.KeyCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 使枚举数前进到 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary`2.KeyCollection" /> 的下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next element; <see langword="false" /> if the enumerator has passed the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 如果枚举数已成功地推进到下一个元素，则为 <see langword="true" />；如果枚举数传递到集合的末尾，则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: After an enumerator is created, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection, and the first call to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method advances the enumerator to the first element of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 创建一个枚举器之后，枚举数定位在集合中，、 首次调用中的第一个元素之前<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法将枚举数推进到集合的第一个元素。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>越过的末尾的集合，枚举数定位在集合中的最后一个元素的后面和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 当枚举器位于此位置上，后续调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>还返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合保持不变，枚举数就保持有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated.
trans-unit.target: 如果更改到集合，如添加、 修改或删除元素，则枚举数将失效。

trans-unit.source: The collection was modified after the enumerator was created.
trans-unit.target: 集合在枚举器创建后被修改。

trans-unit.source: Gets the element at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 获取枚举数当前位置的元素。

trans-unit.source: The element in the collection at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 集合中位于枚举数当前位置的元素。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> property is undefined under any of the following conditions:
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>属性未定义任何以下条件下：

trans-unit.source: The enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection, immediately after the enumerator is created or immediately after the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: 枚举数定位在集合中，第一个元素之前立即创建枚举器之后或紧跟<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A>调用方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method must be called to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>必须调用方法来枚举器向前移动到集合，然后再读取的值的第一个元素<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The last call to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, which indicates the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 上次调用<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`，指示集合的末尾。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> property returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>属性返回相同的对象，直到<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A>调用。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 将 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 设置为下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: If the collection is modified between <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> returns the element that it is set to, even though the enumerator is invalidated.
trans-unit.target: 如果之间修改集合<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>，<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>返回到，设置的元素，即使枚举数已经无效。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator is positioned before the first element of the collection or after the last element.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器位于集合中第一个元素之前或最后一个元素之后。

trans-unit.source: Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 将枚举数设置为其初始位置，该位置位于集合中第一个元素之前。

trans-unit.source: After calling the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> method, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 在调用<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A>方法时，必须调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法将枚举数前移到集合，然后再读取的值的第一个元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.KeyCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合保持不变，枚举数就保持有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated.
trans-unit.target: 如果更改到集合，如添加、 修改或删除元素，则枚举数将失效。

trans-unit.source: The collection was modified after the enumerator was created.
trans-unit.target: 集合在枚举器创建后被修改。
